text: Arturo García (born 3 August 1969) is a Mexican former cyclist. He competed in the team pursuit at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Mexico Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
